🎬 Netflix Movies & TV Shows Clustering
<p align="center"> <img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67974590/217804361-d862f742-dab4-446c-9c58-6e4e396d2259.gif" width="70%"> </p>
📌 Problem Statement

The Netflix Movies and TV Shows dataset contains information about content available on Netflix as of 2019, sourced from Flixable.

According to reports:

📈 TV Shows have tripled since 2010
📉 Movies have decreased by over 2000 titles

👉 This project explores hidden patterns and insights using clustering techniques.

🎯 Goal

The goal of this project is to:

Group similar movies and TV shows using clustering algorithms
Analyze content based on:
Genre
Popularity
Audience type
Help improve:
🎯 Recommendation systems
📊 Content strategy
😊 User engagement
📂 Project Structure
